column5: Anyone know where to get a readable depth map of Minitaki? Thanks!!
I have one that is shaded for depth. It is from Red Lake Digital Media. Phone number is 807-727-3952.
THANKS! Ill give em a call!

I have one from the 80's with spots marked where we caught fish, Waterproof, was used before GPS & fish locators. You can borrow it copy it what ever, I would like them back. I fished there for twenty years 1967 to 87.
That would be incredible- yes please- please let me know what you need from me thanks!
